{"tid":1632954,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［休息是為了走更長遠的路］感謝勇武義士，和理非來接棒","createTime":"2019-10-07T01:24:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T01:26:24.000Z","uid":191139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ff347ccfca8b0e3d5d61913aa26d1a4064f3453a","tid":1632954,"uid":191139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:24:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">支持勇武義士抗爭方式，不割蓆，核爆都唔割</span></span><br />\n<br />\n請聽小弟一言，依家等緊過人權法案，我地抗爭做嘅野基本上都係比國際睇，等外國幫手。<br />\n<br />\n各位勇武義士已經做到好大成效，請你地休息一陣，黎緊呢半個月左右請比我地和理非接棒<br />\n<br />\n和理非建議活動：<br />\n1，商場唱歌<br />\n2，放映會<br />\n3，連儂牆文宣<br />\n4，twitter訊息戰<br />\n<br />\n建議有關活動都係以快閃形式進行<br />\n<br />\n有關活動可再詳細執著<br />\n<br />\n感謝勇武義士，和理非來接棒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57b9caf27dff0ead3565e2d8f5b2094ac64f9966","tid":1632954,"uid":191139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:25:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">感謝勇武義士，和理非來接棒</span>"},{"pid":"07b8834032484d02fa2508a874caf0bcda454bff","tid":1632954,"uid":191139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:25:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">感謝勇武義士，和理非來接棒</span>"},{"pid":"a1746c4fc5711cff83998119d3cdb9eb451f908f","tid":1632954,"uid":191139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:25:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">感謝勇武義士，和理非來接棒</span>"},{"pid":"cb60f341a30d16b59267c4edb4c8c3aab041d687","tid":1632954,"uid":191139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:25:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">感謝勇武義士，和理非來接棒</span>"},{"pid":"89aa2d9f3d9e8a08ce213adc9fef8451c9639242","tid":1632954,"uid":191139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:25:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">感謝勇武義士，和理非來接棒</span>"},{"pid":"b0844d3feb9e00849d1a6fa9cb3fb55a956a4aac","tid":1632954,"uid":191139,"like":0,"d